	abstract = {The presence of water molecules near the selenocysteine residue in the active centre of the GPx enzyme promotes its antioxidant activity. The
              77
              Se NMR chemical shift is sensitive both to the oxidation and the hydration states of the selenium atom.
            
          , 
            
              In this computational work (MP2/aug-cc-pVTZ) we investigated the features of the outer electronic shells of R–SeH, R–Se(−) and R–SeOH fragments (R = CH
              3
